---
const sections = [
  {
    title: "Introduction",
    content:
      "Zao Chat (“we”, “our”, “us”) respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information when you use our platform.",
  },
  {
    title: "Information We Collect",
    content:
      "We may collect personal information such as name, email, phone number, and any data submitted through chatbot interactions. We also collect technical data like IP address, browser type, and usage data.",
  },
  {
    title: "How We Use Information",
    content:
      "We use collected information to provide and improve our services, process leads, communicate with users, and ensure platform security.",
  },
  {
    title: "Lead Data Responsibility",
    content:
      "Customers using Zao Chat are responsible for the data they collect from their website visitors. You must ensure compliance with applicable privacy laws and obtain user consent where required.",
  },
  {
    title: "Cookies & Tracking",
    content:
      "We use cookies and similar technologies to enhance user experience, analyze usage, and improve performance. See our Cookie Policy for more details.",
  },
  {
    title: "Data Sharing",
    content:
      "We do not sell personal data. We may share data with trusted third-party services required to operate the platform (e.g., hosting, analytics, integrations).",
  },
  {
    title: "Data Security",
    content:
      "We implement reasonable security measures to protect your data. However, no system is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.",
  },
  {
    title: "Data Retention",
    content:
      "We retain data only as long as necessary to provide our services and comply with legal obligations.",
  },
  {
    title: "Your Rights",
    content:
      "Depending on your location, you may have rights to access, update, or delete your personal data. Contact us to make such requests.",
  },
  {
    title: "Changes to This Policy",
    content:
      "We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Continued use of the service indicates acceptance of the updated policy.",
  },
];
---

<section class="terms">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="terms-header">
      <span class="section-label">Legal</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">
        Learn how we collect, use, and protect your data.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="terms-list">
      {sections.map((item, i) => (
        <div class="term-item">
          <div class="term-num">
            {(i + 1).toString().padStart(2, "0")}
          </div>
          <div class="term-body">
            <h3>{item.title}</h3>
            <p>{item.content}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* reuse same styles as TermsOfUse */
  .terms { padding: 100px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .terms-header { text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 60px; }
  .section-label { font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--primary); }
  .section-title { font-size: 36px; margin: 10px 0; }
  .section-sub { color: var(--muted); }
  .terms-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 30px; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .term-item { display: flex; gap: 20px; }
  .term-num { font-weight: bold; color: var(--primary); min-width: 40px; }
  .term-body h3 { margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .term-body p { color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }
</style>